      <div
        class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-300"
      >
        <p class="font-semibold">Documentation tip</p>
        <p class="mt-1">
          Write a one-page incident timeline: who/what/when/where + links/screenshots. It helps any official report go
          faster.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
